data.description: Assumable loan; with a full price offer available. Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough. Welcome to your dream ranch-style home in Converse, Texas! This spacious three-bedroom, two-bathroom gem is the epitome of comfortable and modern living. With its open floor plan, ample outdoor space, and sleek interior features, you won't want to miss out on this fantastic opportunity. This home boasts a well-designed open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. You'll love the flow and spaciousness, perfect for entertaining friends. The kitchen is a chef's delight with stunning quartz countertops that offer both durability and elegance. The sleek black appliances provide a modern contrast, making this space as functional as it is stylish.Enjoy the luxury of three generously sized bedrooms, providing plenty of space. Each room offers comfort and style, making it easy to create your own personal retreat. With two full bathrooms, you'll have the convenience and privacy you need. The primary bathroom is a true oasis, featuring modern fixtures and finishes. Step outside to your expansive backyard, fully fenced for privacy and security. The outdoor space is perfect to play freely, and it's an ideal canvas for gardening and outdoor activities. Don't miss your chance to make this beautiful ranch-style home in Converse, TX, your own. It's the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. Schedule a viewing today and experience the lifestyle you've been dreaming of!
